Name Inside the Mountain~
Desc You are in front of a beautiful golden cave carved into the side of the 
mountain.  An area of ten feet around the cave has been cleared to prevent 
any hostile creatures from entering.  When you look down the stairs in the 
cave, you notice from the thick layer of dust upon them that they have not 
been used much recently.  On the northern end of the cave there is a large 
golden gate.  
~
RoomFlags dark no_mob~
Sector cave~
Exit down 11601
End


#11601
Name Entrance to the Tombs of Tarin~
Desc The marble stairs lead into the Tombs of Tarin.  Large boulders from the 
roof have destroyed part of the stairs, but it seems safe enough to climb 
down the next few feet.  A bronze plate has been nailed to the roof above 
the stairs.  You can go up and down from here.  
~
RoomFlags dark no_mob~
Sector cave~
Exit up 11600
Exit down 11602
End


#11602
Name Upper Half of the Broken Stairs~
Desc You find yourself standing at the edge of what once was the marble stairs 
leading into the tomb.  Enormous boulders have wrecked the stairs below, and 
if you decide to take the jump down, it seems impossible to get up again.  
You can go down and up from here.  
~
RoomFlags dark~
Sector cave~
Exit up 11601
Exit down 11603
End


#11603
