#11604
Name Vault of Heros~
Desc You enter a huge hall occupied with stone statues of long forgotten heroes.  
The statues seem indestructible, and hanging from each one is a small gold 
plate with some writing on it.  Besides the dust and the dry air, this room 
amazes you with its beauty.  
~
RoomFlags dark~
Sector cave~
Exit west 11605
End


#11605
Name Entrance Hall of Tarin~
Desc Below the stairs you find this beautiful hall made out of stone.  Large 
banners hang from the roof and on each banner an eagle is painted.  In the 
middle of the hall you find a well springing with crystal clear water.  
Around the well there are small bottles hanging with ropes attached to them. 
 To the east you see a pair of large bronze doors leading into the vault of 
heroes.  And to the west, there is a large door that opens with a gate that 
lifts.  The hall continues into the darkness to the north and to the south.  

~
RoomFlags dark~
Sector cave~
Exit east 11604
Exit up 11603
End


